PRICE REDUCTION**
 
 
****PRICED TO MOVE***
 
This 1500 Ranch house sits nestled back in the woods,over a wonderful small water bridge and in a great area of North Pole. Surrounded by a large yard perfect for all your well planned outdoor activities it has plenty of room for what every you need to do or park! You will find the back yard is fenced in, perfect for your fur babies and/or kids, the side yard has a dog run that is great year round. This ranch style house has updated bathrooms and plenty of storage. The open dining and living area is perfect for entertaining and you can walk outside onto your trex deck for additional entertaining in the back yard. 3 bedrooms, 2 bath come check out your next North Pole home! *Schedule your showing today
